### Ascend API — File Uploads
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT
@goalId = REPLACE_WITH_GOAL_UUID
@habitId = REPLACE_WITH_HABIT_UUID
@fileId = REPLACE_WITH_FILE_UUID

# ─── Avatar ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Upload or replace profile avatar (JPEG/PNG/WebP, max 5 MB)
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads/avatar
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="avatar.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./sample-avatar.jpg

###

# ─── Goal motivation images ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Upload a motivation image for a goal (e.g. grade screenshot, vision board)
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads/goal/{{goalId}}/image
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="grade_95.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./sample-grade.jpg

###

### List all motivation images for a goal
GET {{baseUrl}}/uploads/goal/{{goalId}}/images
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# ─── Habit evidence ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Upload habit evidence image (workout photo, book page, etc.)
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads/habit/{{habitId}}/evidence
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="workout_proof.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./sample-proof.jpg

###

### List all evidence images for a habit
GET {{baseUrl}}/uploads/habit/{{habitId}}/evidence
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# ─── General file upload ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Upload a general file (image or PDF)
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads/file
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="certificate.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./sample-certificate.pdf

###

# ─── File listing ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### List all my uploaded files
GET {{baseUrl}}/uploads/files
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List only goal motivation files
GET {{baseUrl}}/uploads/files?context=GOAL_MOTIVATION
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List only habit evidence files
GET {{baseUrl}}/uploads/files?context=HABIT_EVIDENCE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# ─── File deletion ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Delete an uploaded file (removes from Cloudinary + DB)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/uploads/files/{{fileId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
